wer\">\r\n\r\nModify the main features of the website on WordPress\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n 	<li class=\"css-1ifkymy\"><span class=\"css-ny32s2\" aria-hidden=\"true\">•</span>\r\n<div class=\"rc-CML unified-CML\" dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div class=\"css-g2bbpm\" data-testid=\"cml-viewer\">\r\n\r\nAdd pages to the website on WordPress\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div class=\"css-6fogz8\">\r\n<div class=\"css-5a2hyw\">\r\n<h4 class=\"css-6ecy9b\">Recommended experience</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rc-CML unified-CML\" dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div class=\"css-g2bbpm\" data-testid=\"cml-viewer\">\r\n\r\nThe learner would need to know how to use an Internet Browser\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"css-6fogz8\">\r\n<div class=\"css-5a2hyw\">\r\n<h4 class=\"css-6ecy9b\">5 project images</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"cds-9 css-16obph7 cds-10\">\r\n 	<li class=\"cds-9 css-0 cds-11 cds-grid-item cds-50 cds-61\"><button class=\"css-12mj5lo\" type=\"button\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-app=\"unified_description_page\" data-track-page=\"consumer_project_page\" data-track-action=\"click\" data-track-component=\"image_gallery_expand\" aria-label=\"Click to expand item\"><img class=\"css-151gbcv\" src=\"https://d3njjcbhbojbot.cloudfront.net/api/utilities/v1/imageproxy/https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/rhyme/imported-screenshots/5nrlGXoYEeyxdQr9VwEEHw/0.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;dpr=1&amp;w=200&amp;h=150&amp;fit=crop\" srcset=\"https://d3njjcbhbojbot.cloudfront.net/api/utilities/v1/imageproxy/https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/rhyme/imported-screenshots/5nrlGXoYEeyxdQr9VwEEHw/0.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;dpr=2&amp;w=200&amp;h=150&amp;fit=crop 2x, https://d3njjcbhbojbot.cloudfront.net/api/utilities/v1/imageproxy/https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/rhyme/imported-screenshots/5nrlGXoYEeyxdQr9VwEEHw/0.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;dpr=3&amp;w=200&amp;h=150&amp;fit=crop 3x\" alt=\"\" /></button></li>\r\n 	<li c