 interested in learning the fundamentals of AI.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"css-4s48ix\">In this module, you will learn the definition of AI and the basics of generative AI. You will explore the impact, applications, and use cases of AI and how it is transforming our lives. Additionally, you will discover common tools and applications of generative AI. You will learn about AI agents and smart assistants and their common use cases. Finally, you will examine how AI is reshaping various industries and sectors.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"css-15ko5n9\">\r\n<div class=\"css-5a2hyw\">\r\n<h4 class=\"css-6ecy9b\">What\'s included</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"css-kqm948\"><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">12 videos</span><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">2 readings</span><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">3 assignments</span><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">1 app item</span><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">1 discussion prompt</span><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">3 plugins</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"cds-react-aria2203193674-:r25:\" class=\"css-xp0srt\" aria-label=\"Info about module content\"><button id=\"cds-react-aria2203193674-:r25:-cta\" class=\"cds-149 cds-ShowMoreContainer-ctaButton cds-button-disableElevation cds-button-ghost css-11hc1hy\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"cds-react-aria2203193674-:r25:-content\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-label=\"Info about module content\"><span class=\"cds-button-label\">Hide info about module content</span></button>\r\n<div class=\"cds-187 cds-188\">\r\n<div class=\"cds-190\">\r\n<div class=\"cds-191\">\r\n<div id=\"cds-react-aria2203193674-:r25:-content\" class=\"cds-ShowMoreContainer-content cds-ShowMoreContainer-silent\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" aria-labelledby=\"cds-react-aria2203193674-:r25:-cta\">\r\n<div class=\"css-15ko5n9\">\r\n<div class=\"css-5a2hyw\">\r\n<h5 class=\"css-h81u6c\"><span class=\"css-1gn6gmm\">12 videos</span><span class=\"css-1oocsie\" aria-hidden=\"true\">•</span>Total 79 minutes</h5>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=